OL,3,CHill farmers' finances 'in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHill farmers, who are among England's
OL,8,Fpoorest, face an "outsized" hit to
OL,9,Flivelihoods from delays to new farming
OL,10,Fschemes, a think tank has warned.
OL,12,FEfforts to tackle climate change,
OL,13,Frestore nature and curb flood risk in
OL,14,Flower-lying areas are also threatened
OL,15,Fby a lack of new nature-friendly
OL,16,Ffarming payments to upland areas, the
OL,17,FEnergy and Climate Intelligence Unit
OL,18,F(ECIU) said.
