OL,3,CHill farmers' finances 'in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAnalysis by the ECIU has shown that
OL,8,Fhill farmers are only receiving 8% or
OL,9,F#39 million of the Government's new
OL,10,Ffarming support scheme, the
OL,11,Fsustainable farming incentive (SFI),
OL,12,Fdespite accounting for 15% of
OL,13,FEngland's area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
