OL,3,CHill farmers' finances 'in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAnd there have been repeated delays to
OL,8,Foverhauling and expanding another part
OL,9,Fof the new farming payments programme,
OL,10,Fthe Countryside Stewardship "higher
OL,11,Ftier" scheme for creating woodlands
OL,12,Fand other habitat, which will be key
OL,13,Fto supporting upland farms, the ECIU
OL,14,Fsaid.
