OL,3,CHill farmers' finances 'in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FOne upland farmer warned he did not
OL,8,Fknow what "hill farmers will do" if
OL,9,Fthey could not get on to the more
OL,10,Fambitious, higher-paying schemes as
OL,11,Fold EU subsidies are phased out ` and
OL,12,Fthat nature and climate would also
OL,13,Fsuffer.
OL,15,FSince Brexit, agricultural subsidies
OL,16,Fwhich mainly paid landowners for the
OL,17,Famount of land farmed are being
OL,18,Fchanged to environmental land
OL,19,Fmanagement scheme (Elms) payments for
OL,20,F"public goods" such as creating
OL,21,Fhabitat, healthy soils and clean water.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@`O]|D@AOU|D@NO]
