OL,3,CHill farmers' finances 'in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FElms consists of three tiers ` the
OL,8,FSFI, the Countryside Stewardship
OL,9,Fhigher tier scheme, and a large-scale
OL,10,Flandscape recovery scheme involving
OL,11,Fgroups of landowners.
OL,13,FThe Government has prioritised the
OL,14,Fdevelopment and delivery of the SFI,
OL,15,Fas it is most relevant to the majority
OL,16,Fof farmers, but the options landowners
OL,17,Fcan implement in return for payments
OL,18,Funder the scheme are less well suited
OL,19,Fto hill farmers ` who have among the
OL,20,Flowest incomes ` the think tank warned.
