OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAnd the Countryside Stewardship's
OL,8,Fhigher tier scheme was repeatedly
OL,9,Fdelayed under previous governments,
OL,10,Fafter problems since its initial
OL,11,Flaunch in 2015, and is not due to be
OL,12,Favailable until next summer.
OL,14,FThere are also fears not enough
OL,15,Ffarmers will be able to get into it
OL,16,Fwhen it does launch.
