OL,4,Cfrom delays to new farming schemes `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe ECIU said a big increase in
OL,8,Fspending and uptake of the higher tier
OL,9,Fscheme is needed to meet targets to
OL,10,Freverse declines in nature and curb
OL,11,Femissions by increasing woodland cover
OL,12,Fand restoring peatland to store carbon.
OL,14,FIn 2024, the uplands received 42%,
OL,15,Fsome #50 million, of the remaining
OL,16,Fpayments under the Countryside
OL,17,FStewardship's predecessor scheme,
OL,18,Fshowing how important that element of
OL,19,Fthe programme will be to hill farmers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
