OL,8,Fanalyst at the ECIU, said: "Hill
OL,9,Ffarmers are often not rich and are
OL,10,Fless likely to be affected by changes
OL,11,Fto inheritance tax, but delays to new
OL,12,FGovernment schemes could have an
OL,13,Foutsized negative impact on their
OL,14,Flivelihoods.
