OL,7,F"The Countryside Stewardship higher-
OL,8,Ftier scheme, designed to support
OL,9,Ffarmers to create and restore habitats
OL,10,Flike woodlands, which would help to
OL,11,Freduce flood risk downstream, has been
OL,12,Frepeatedly delayed under previous
OL,13,Fgovernments.
OL,15,F"Any further delays will put hill
OL,16,Ffarmers' finances in jeopardy."
