OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FNeil Heseltine, an upland farmer and
OL,8,Fmember of the Nature Friendly Farming
OL,9,FNetwork from Malham in North
OL,10,FYorkshire, said hill farmers were
OL,11,F"ready, willing and able" to do more
OL,12,Ffor nature and climate change on their
OL,13,Fland, but the support has not been
OL,14,Fthere for them.
OL,16,FHe added: "I don't begrudge our
OL,17,Flowland peers the funding they're
OL,18,Fgetting, I just want some of it to
OL,19,Fflow up the hill to allow us to do the
OL,20,Fsame.
