OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"If it doesn't, climate and nature
OL,8,Fwill suffer.
OL,10,F"And as the old subsidies are phased
OL,11,Fout, I don't know what hill farmers
OL,12,Fwill do if we can't get into these
OL,13,Fmore ambitious, higher-paying, higher-
OL,14,Ftier schemes we've long been promised."
OL,16,FMr Heseltine said the new team at the
OL,17,FEnvironment Department (Defra) needed
OL,18,Fto ensure the promised schemes were
OL,19,Favailable as soon as possible.
