OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCommenting on the analysis, Harry
OL,8,FBowell, director of land and nature at
OL,9,Fthe National Trust, said: "Hill
OL,10,Ffarmers ` many of whom are National
OL,11,FTrust tenants ` are ideally placed to
OL,12,Fdeliver big gains for nature alongside
OL,13,Ffarming, and deserve to be rewarded
OL,14,Fproperly for this work.
OL,16,F"We want to see an urgent roll out and
OL,17,Fproper resourcing of Countryside
OL,18,FStewardship higher tier schemes, to
OL,19,Fsupport farmers in the uplands to
OL,20,Fcarry out this vital role."
